SUMMARY
=======

A small python application that uses the serial port of a Jeelink or some other serially attached Arduino with a RFM12b module to recieve dat afrom remote RFM12B units using the OpenEnergyMonitor/TinyTX protocol.

INSTALL
=======

mkdir /usr/local/mqtt-rfm12b/ /etc/mqtt-rfm12b/
cd /usr/local/
git clone git://github.com/kylegordon/mqtt-rfm12b.git
cp mqtt-rfm12b.init /etc/init.d/mqtt-rfm12b
update-rc.d mqtt-rfm12b defaults
cp mqtt-rfm12b.default /etc/default/mqtt-rfm12b
/etc/init.d/mqtt-rfm12b start

